    <header>
        <img src="/img/skiesBackground.webp" alt="mountain" class="background">
        <h1 class="titleSnowboards animate__animated animate__zoomIn">Skis</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="snowboardCards">
        <div class="OptionsCards">
            <h5 class="titleFilters">Skis</h5>
            <div class="filterOpcions">
                <h6 class="filtersTitle">Filters</h6>
                <label class="cyberpunk-checkbox-label">
                    <input type="checkbox" class="cyberpunk-checkbox" value="PriceUp">
                    Price Up
                </label>
                <label class="cyberpunk-checkbox-label">
                    <input type="checkbox" class="cyberpunk-checkbox"  value="PriceDown">
                    Price down
                </label>
                <label class="cyberpunk-checkbox-label">
                    <input type="checkbox" class="cyberpunk-checkbox" value="Newest">
                    Newest
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cards">
            {{#each products}}
                <div class="cardProduct" style="background-image: url('../img/products/{{imageFront}}'); background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-repeat: no-repeat;">
                    <div class="card-details">
                        <p class="text-title">{{title}}</p>
                        <p class="text-body">{{price}} usd</p>
                    </div>
                    <a class="card-button" href="/product/{{_id}}">More info</a>
                </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="aboutSection">
        <div class="aboutContent">
            <h2>Experience the Peak of Skiing Excellence</h2>
            <p>
                In the realm of skiing excellence, our collection stands tall as a testament to uncompromised quality and unparalleled experience. Each ski is meticulously crafted, a fusion of artistry and engineering, ensuring an exceptional performance on the snow-laden slopes. Our commitment to delivering top-tier products is evident in every detail. From the cutting-edge materials that form the core to the precise engineering behind each curve, our skis are a symphony of innovation and durability. Crafted for seasoned professionals and aspiring enthusiasts alike, they epitomize the pinnacle of skiing mastery. Whether you seek the thrill of fresh powder or the challenge of steep descents, our skis embody the perfect balance between control and agility. Designed to enhance your prowess on the mountains, they bring forth an unmatched experience that embraces both precision and exhilaration. Our dedication to perfecting the skiing experience extends beyond the tangible; it is an ethos reflected in the heart and soul of every ski we offer. Dive into our range of meticulously designed skis and discover a world where craftsmanship meets adventure, where precision meets excitement, and where every slope becomes an opportunity for boundless exploration and mastery.
            </p>

        </div>
    </section>

